{"tid":2450643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2100 眾新聞 中國組 美國《香港自治法》報告 中美會談前夕 國務卿布林肯點名譚耀宗等24官員損香港自治","createTime":"2021-03-17T14:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T01:13:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f376264630c6303e7be8b54c93417d5538d0019","tid":2450643,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"2100 眾新聞 中國組<br />\n美國《香港自治法》報告 中美會談前夕 國務卿布林肯點名譚耀宗等24官員損香港自治｜<br />\n北京禁補習社實體課 導師：轉到酒店上｜<br />\n青島海星氾濫成災捉都捉不完 內地網民：蒸了吃 <br />\n（眾新聞 中國組） #眾新聞中國組​<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8-zkQK1bvkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8-zkQK1bvkc&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=f7cbadd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8-zkQK1bvkc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n72.5K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n🔸中美高層會面前夕，美方重提損害香港自治的官員名單。有學者分析指對中美會面影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n🔸北京官方禁部分地區開實體補習課，有補習導師表示另有對策，或會轉到酒店上課。<br />\n<br />\n🔸青島膠州灣海星氾濫成災，料造成1億經濟損失，有網民提議把海星蒸了吃。<br />\n<br />\n訂閱我們：<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subs...​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Faboutus%2F%23subs...%E2%80%8B&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=96bb9ecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subs...​</a><br />\n<br />\n#中美高層會面​ #損害香港自治​ #補習課​ #海星氾濫"},{"pid":"ba8972087bf4c90a97e457c60f1ef4182ae59247","tid":2450643,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1418b966b8c8b6486c7ad49f41808daba2d3b07b","tid":2450643,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:42:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e851c6c81d6f6f47362af6290c3925bf43d84520","tid":2450643,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"20210317"}]}